#

Baked Sweet Potato with Greek Yogurt and Chives

55 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

A nutritious and delicious baked sweet potato topped with creamy Greek yogurt and fresh chives.

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 medium
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • chives: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
